<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/wes-streeting> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Wes Streeting was Secretary of State for Health and Social Care from 5 July 2024 to 14 May 2026. He was elected as the MP for Ilford North in July 2024."@en .
